cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification (re-id) using video-based representation. The most relevant sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV) as the paper deals with image and video analysis. The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as distance learning and optimization, which are relevant to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the problem of occlusion and pose, which are related to the sub-category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
